-For DVD support

Install libdvdnav4, libdvdread4, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly, and libdvd-pkg.

Run the command

sudo dpkg-reconfigure libdvd-pkg

---

List of apps to install - zsh vim mc grsync vlc krusader thunderbird libreoffice-fresh xsane qbittorrent kolour-paint gimp

- SSH Keys

ssh-keygen -t ed25519
then
ssh-copy-id rob@server-ip

---

- Numlock on during boot

Add Numlock=on to /etc/sddm.conf

---

-Install youtube-dl

sudo wget https://yt-dl.org/downloads/latest/youtube-dl -O /usr/local/bin/youtube-dl
$ sudo chmod a+rx /usr/local/bin/youtube-dl

youtube-dl --help 
youtube-dl file-link

---

Install oxygen
Install kdeplasma-addons

---

Install “plasma-widgets-addons” package

---

Install “kwin-decoration-oxygen”

---

-To fix wifi dropping

in /etc/default/grub on the GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX line add ipv6.disable=1 then run
sudo update-grub
(and reboot)

